commit.message:
Allow 10 gigabit speed throttles

This commit increases max upload and download speed by 16 times. It allows utilization of 10 gigabit connections.
Fix memory access crash with socket_address object

configure: Define _GNU_SOURCE when checking for pthread_setname_np

Previously, the test would always fail with compilers that do not
support implicit function declarations because the pthread_setname_np
function was not declared.
